  "texts": [
    "The Closeness Centrality, TrustRank, DIAMOnD, and DIGEST tools were tested in a two-stage evaluation process.",
    "For each tool, 100 = specific questions were manually curated, for which both an API call and the generated result were available.",
    "In the first stage, it was checked whether the LLM called the respective API correctly and optimally so that accuracy could be determined on this basis (Call-Accuracy).",
    "In the second stage, a manual validation was performed to assess whether the agent correctly interpreted and processed the returned results in terms of content (Answer-Accuracy).",
    "To evaluate the NeDRex KG tool, we checked for 174 questions to determine whether the result set returned by the agent represents a superset of the silver standard annotations created by human experts."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}